        <span class="" id="parent-fieldname-title-214a194418e042019f057c10a1e21827">
            When Crafts Become Activism: A More Beautiful Movement
        </span>
    
        </h1>

                                    <div id="content-description" class="article-description">
            
        <span class="" id="parent-fieldname-subheadline-214a194418e042019f057c10a1e21827">
